flowchart TD
    ENTRY([Candidate Entry]) --> M1{MANDATORY 1\nDI Direction}
    M1 -->|LONG: +DI > -DI| M2{MANDATORY 2\nFVG Size >= 5 ticks}
    M1 -->|SHORT: -DI > +DI| M2
    M1 -->|Fail| REJECT([REJECT])

    M2 -->|Pass| OPT[OPTIONAL FILTERS\nNeed 2 of 3 to pass]
    M2 -->|Fail| REJECT

    OPT --> O1{Displacement\n>= 1.0x avg body}
    OPT --> O2{ADX >= 11\nor 3x disp + ADX >= 10}
    OPT --> O3{EMA Trend\nEMA20 vs EMA50}

    O1 -->|Pass| COUNT[Count Passes]
    O1 -->|Fail| COUNT
    O2 -->|Pass| COUNT
    O2 -->|Fail| COUNT
    O3 -->|Pass| COUNT
    O3 -->|Fail| COUNT

    COUNT --> CHECK{Passes >= 2?}
    CHECK -->|Yes| TIME[Time Filters]
    CHECK -->|No| REJECT

    TIME --> T1{Midday Cutoff\n12:00-14:00?}
    T1 -->|In range| REJECT
    T1 -->|Outside| T2{NQ/MNQ PM\nAfter 14:00?}
    T2 -->|Yes + NQ| REJECT
    T2 -->|No| RISK{Min Risk Check\nES: 1.5 pts, NQ: 6 pts}
    RISK -->|Pass| ACCEPT([ACCEPT])
    RISK -->|Fail| REJECT
